## Development Notes

### Extending BC27:
1. **Follow dependency model** - Never reverse dependencies
2. **Use events** - No hard module references
3. **Table Extensions** - Don't modify core tables
4. **Page Extensions** - Add fields to existing pages
5. **Event Subscribers** - Hook into core logic

### Common Patterns:
```al
// Table Extension (recommended)
tableextension 77100 "ABC Customer" extends Customer
{
    fields
    {
        field(77100; "ABC Custom Field"; Text[50]) { }
    }
}

// Event Subscriber (loosely coupled)
[EventSubscriber(ObjectType::Codeunit, Codeunit::"Sales-Post", 'OnBeforePostSalesDoc', '', false, false)]
local procedure OnBeforePostSalesDoc(var SalesHeader: Record "Sales Header")
begin
    // Custom logic
end;
```

